text: Ani unako samudayaka kaphiraharuko nayakaharule bhanna thaleh ki hamile timila'i aphu jastai e'uta manisako rupama dekhchaum ra yo pani dekhchaum ki timra anuyayiharu tallo srenika manisaharu baheka kohi chaina jasale najani bujhikana timro anuyayi bha'eka chan. Hamile ta hamiharubhanda timima kehi badhi visesata dekheka chainaum baru timila'i hamile jhutha thandachaum
